(33, 'What is a common downside of two-phase commit?', 'backend', 'mcq', 'hard', 'No coordination needed', 'Higher availability', 'Coordinator is a single point of failure and slow', 'Better latency', 2, '2PC adds latency and a coordinator SPOF.', ARRAY['distributed','transactions']),
